{"tid":1451144,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"機場集會有人擊鼓帶節奏嗌口號，效果會好好多！","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T01:35:05.000Z","uid":67465,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"35ead036046803ed6eb8c5facbde9831570266d7","tid":1451144,"uid":67465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:45.000Z","msg":"我第一次機場集會同埋11/8 都有去，<br />\n第一次去嘅時候keep 住有手足擊鼓，嗌口號好齊，同埋都鼓勵到好多人跟住鼓聲keep 住嗌落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但今日冇咗擊鼓手，變得呢到一堆聲嗰到一堆聲，<br />\n我自己靜落嚟聽嘅時候發覺係完全聽唔到嗌緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望今日12/8可以出現番一個擊鼓手lead 住大家嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，除咗塞爆機場齊齊和你飛之外，都可以有效convey 番我哋嘅訊息比遊客！！<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以帶個鼓去啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外就係講到口都臭<br />\n盡量嗌番英文或者普通話嘅口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位機場見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb31d6094d7f38b6d1c26055ca0858e8510e021b","tid":1451144,"uid":67465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:26:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef5a72af5371a7852920858e80fd43d349c3a5e2","tid":1451144,"uid":67465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:26:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"316379825462053a8df5da101f202ab6cdeebd09","tid":1451144,"uid":67465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:27:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c500eb463512ad69895a919ddf6d4f877b016b3","tid":1451144,"uid":65888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:27:52.000Z","msg":"Agger平時叫口號真係好易亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dabbd9f0086ed779bbfd78ee234267383d36964","tid":1451144,"uid":67465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08